Changed Connect REST API Response Bodies

Configuration Load Instance (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Configuration Set Instance (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Product Set Quantity (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Configurator Add Nodes (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Configurator Update Nodes (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Configurator Delete Nodes (POST) - new property: configuratorUIModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.

Configuration (POST) - new property: uiModifications—Map of a sales transaction ID and a list of configurator UI modifications.
